    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      102.56,
      543.16,
      116.18
    ],
    "text": "The primary relief sought by the Petitioner is for a writ of Certiorari quashing the certificate,",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      123.44,
      543.16,
      137.06
    ],
    "text": "marked P8(e), wherein the 2nd Respondent has invoked the provisions of the Offences",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.960000038146973,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      144.2,
      543.14,
      157.82
    ],
    "text": "Against Public Property Act No. 12 of 1982, as amended (Act). The said P8(e) is a",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      164.96,
      543.12,
      178.58
    ],
    "text": "certificate issued in terms of Section 8(1) of the Act by which the 2nd Respondent-Assistant",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      6.960000038146973,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      185.72,
      543.09,
      199.34
    ],
    "text": "Superintendent of Police has certified that the money belonging to the Provident Fund",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      206.48,
      543.16,
      220.1
    ],
    "text": "(Fund) of the Coconut Cultivation Board and the money in credit of the said Fund which is",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      227.24,
      542.89,
      240.86
    ],
    "text": "alleged to have been misappropriated by the Petitioner is public property and the value of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      248.0,
      304.55,
      261.62
    ],
    "text": "such public property is above Rs.500,000.00.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      268.91,
      543.16,
      296.33
    ],
    "text": "What needs consideration of this Court is whether the money lying in credit of the Fund can",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      303.47,
      543.15,
      317.09
    ],
    "text": "be considered as public property which comes within the relevant definition of the Act. The",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      324.23,
      543.16,
      337.85
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner claims that the Fund has been established in terms of Section 27(1) of Employees",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      344.99,
      543.05,
      358.61
    ],
    "text": "Provident Fund Act No.15 of 1958 (as amended). The Petitioners contention is that the Fund",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      365.87,
      542.94,
      379.49
    ],
    "text": "is a private fund and it is not affiliated to the Employees Provident Fund established under",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      386.63,
      287.51,
      400.25
    ],
    "text": "the said Employees Provident Fund Act.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      407.39,
      542.95,
      434.81
    ],
    "text": "The document, marked P3, is the constitution of the Fund and in terms of the said",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      441.97,
      543.14,
      455.59
    ],
    "text": "constitution, the Coconut Cultivation Board (Board) being the employer contributes on",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      462.85,
      542.86,
      476.47
    ],
    "text": "regular basis to the Fund along with the employees of the Board. Every month contributions",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      483.61,
      542.94,
      497.23
    ],
    "text": "by the employees and the employer are being deposited in favour of the Fund in terms of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      504.37,
      181.64,
      517.99
    ],
    "text": "Clause 10(1) of P3.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      525.13,
      542.83,
      552.55
    ],
    "text": "The argument of the Petitioner is that the money belonging to and earned by the Fund is in",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      559.81,
      543.07,
      573.43
    ],
    "text": "trust for the persons to whom the money belongs. Further, the Petitioner contends that the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      580.57,
      542.83,
      594.19
    ],
    "text": "Act does not cover a statutory board acting in the capacity of a trustee holding money",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      601.36,
      543.03,
      614.98
    ],
    "text": "belonging to a private entity. The Petitioner relies on the judgement of Trade Exchange",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT",
      "Calisto MT,BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      622.48,
      543.07,
      636.1
    ],
    "text": "(Ceylon) Ltd vs. Asian Hotels Corporation Ltd (1981) 1 Sri. L.R. 67 where it was held that the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT",
      "Calisto MT,BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      643.6,
      542.95,
      657.22
    ],
    "text": "Asian Hotels Corporation Ltd cannot be considered as an agent of the government for the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      664.36,
      542.86,
      677.98
    ],
    "text": "mere reason that most of the capital of the said corporation had been contributed by the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      685.24,
      389.05,
      698.86
    ],
    "text": "government or the shares were controlled by the government.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      731.38,
      542.6,
      755.86
    ],
    "text": "Page 4 of 6",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri-Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      71.94,
      542.91,
      85.56
    ],
    "text": "It is abundantly clear that the property of the Statutory Boards and Public Corporations are",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      92.72,
      543.11,
      106.34
    ],
    "text": "within the definition of public property under the said Act. The said Board has been",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      113.48,
      543.16,
      127.1
    ],
    "text": "incorporated by virtue of the Coconut Development Act No. 46 of 1971 (as amended). Thus,",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      134.24,
      543.16,
      147.86
    ],
    "text": "it is no doubt that the money belonging to the Board is well within the purview of the Act and",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      155.12,
      543.16,
      168.74
    ],
    "text": "the dicta of the above judgement has no relevancy to the instant Application. Anyhow, the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      175.88,
      543.13,
      189.5
    ],
    "text": "issue here is whether the money held by the Board in the capacity as a trustee or as a guardian",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      196.64,
      543.16,
      210.26
    ],
    "text": "would become public property under the Act. Both, the learned Presidents Counsel for the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      217.4,
      542.99,
      231.02
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner and the learned Deputy Solicitor General for the Respondents made submissions",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      238.16,
      542.84,
      251.78
    ],
    "text": "on the above point of law. Now, I must consider whether this Court could resolve this issue",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      258.95,
      437.77,
      272.57
    ],
    "text": "at this threshold stage without calling for affidavits of the Respondents.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calisto MT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      279.71,
      535.0,
